div.span:
There's... trees. And I wandered by a rusty theme park ride
half sunken in the dirt. Must have been there for a hundred
years. I guess someone else thought this place needed some
entertainment.

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
Sorry, sir, our lines are busy at the moment--I think I'm
going to have to put you on hold. Until next time?

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
I would listen to it gurgling and humming as my heart beat
loud in my ears. And I'd pretend it was a train chugging
really fast. A train that didn't need a track, bulldozing
through the trees and mountains.

div.span: Anyway... I finished reading the document of all history.

div.span: Mr. [playerLastName], did you learn anything from your life on Earth?

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
Sir, I'm sorry. I tried to tell you about Mr. Sob. But I
waited too long, and we lost connection.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
By the way, while I was reading, Shrimp snuck his way out
through the elevator shaft, barked at me, and bounded out
through the broken window. I guess he's free now because of
you.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
When I got to the present time, I saw the document was
writing itself! The paper was growing to make more space. I
wish I could have done that on my math homework.

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span: Oh, and what about the last human alive?

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span: Oh. I guess I learned I should believe in rumors about haunted truckers.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span: I'll spare you the grizzly details.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
Ha, not how I thought the human race would go out! But I'm
not sure what I expected.

div.span:
When I got to the present time, I saw the document was
writing itself! The paper was growing to make more space. I
wish I could have done that on my math homework.

div.span: Sir? I can barely hear you.

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
The sky darkened, and the trees are all bent in one
direction. It's almost like they're bowing down!

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
When I was alive, when I was scared of the dark at night, I
would watch the water heater that stood outside my bedroom
door. It was towering and immovable, like... like a water
heater.

I haven't been outside in the afterlife for some 40 years.
Now I feel like a kid who ran outside to see the fireworks.

Congratulations, Mr. [playerLastName]. This is a momentous
occasion. Shame I left my party poppers at my desk.

I don't think we're going to knock into each other, Mr.
[playerLastName]. This forest is too big!

I pretended the Upturned Inn was a normal hotel after he
turned it into some kind of death trap. I ''turned a blind
eye'', as they say! Haha...

div.span:
I finally decided I'd rather wander out here than be in that
rotten building. I've lied to myself about it too long.

div.span:
The human race did all it could. And look what it got. A
bad-luck sundae with a nasty cherry on top--except instead
of vanilla ice cream, it's probably just a heap of
mayonnaise, or shaving cream.

div.span:
They stayed alive for a few weeks. Then two of them got into
an argument over who had dibs on a bag of chips...

div.span: Well, you passed!

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
I guess that's it, then. We know how you, I, and the human
race all came to an end.

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span: AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH!

div.span: On the bright side, do you remember the friendship survey I forced you to take?

rect.style: fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px;

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span: ...which spiraled into murder. They both died.

g.style: border-block-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-inline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); caret-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(204, 204, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); fill: rgb(13, 0, 50); font-family: 'trebuchet ms', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; outline-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px; stroke: rgb(42, 0, 168); stroke-width: 5px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-emphasis-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);

span.style: padding-block: 5px; padding: 5px; padding-inline: 5px;

div.span:
I don't think there's any use running! Or hiding. I've
wasted my whole life hiding. Maybe I'll just say hello?

div.span: And I feel something big approaching this way.

Whatever is in this forest with us, it's bigger than you,
that's for sure. You're about an inch tall!
